{"tid":1652633,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"請停止裝修","createTime":"2019-10-13T17:49:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T18:37:45.000Z","uid":277301,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f2cda8d6b0db17a7d801895050ed8d45ecb0b745","tid":1652633,"uid":277301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T17:49:04.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">停你老母</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>擔心輿論？ 裝修好似好暴力？</strong></span><br />\n小弟有個建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為每次裝修都一定會有路人影相<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>但係文宣真係好重要</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: navy;\">真係要咁多人擔遮遮住咩？</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不如搵人拎住文宣係裝修既時候對外解釋點解要裝修啦</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">再搵多個做time marker 同哨兵</span><br />\n每次裝修都係冇乜共識咁有個人嗌走先<br />\n不如搵一個人控制時間 同埋一個控制地理位置啦"},{"pid":"a5bf7d773429e23f8b1e195de24a143a99d079be","tid":1652633,"uid":91432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T18:37:45.000Z","msg":"閱。"}]}